%h2 Headings

%p Headings are based off the typographic scale and include a <code>margin-bottom</code> of <code>24</code> pixels and the appropriate <code>font-weight</code>.

%h5 Mixins &amp; Classes

%p As with the general typographic scale, headings also have the approrpriate mixins and classes which start with <code>.h-*</code> instead of <code>.s-*</code> for scale. Mixin example: <code>+h-alpha</code>, <code>+h-bravo</code>, <code>+h-charlie</code>, and etc. Class example: <code>.h-alpha</code>, <code>.h-bravo</code>, <code>.h-charlie</code>, and etc.


