-# ========================================
-# Font weights

%h2 Font Weights

%p There are three font weights available, and a few rules as to how these font weights may be paired with each font family. Open Sans may only appear as italic in a normal or bold weight, not book. Source Code Pro should never appear in a book weight or italic. Note: There aren&#8217;t any variables, mixins, or classes for these values. They must be used outright.

%ul.sg-value-list
  %li.sg-type-weight-bold
    Bold
    %code.sg-value-offset 600
  %li.sg-type-weight-normal
    Normal
    %code.sg-value-offset 400
  %li.sg-type-weight-book
    Book
    %code.sg-value-offset 300

